These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, prince, siglo
1. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
2. the siglo-smoker is between the chaman-smoker and the prince-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Cigar   | chaman | siglo | prince |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, pink, light-blue
1. the person who likes purple is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes light-blue##2
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Color   | light-blue | purple | pink |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different games are played: snooker, domino, mah-jongg
1. the person playing domino is between the person playing snooker and the person playing mah-jongg##2
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | domino | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, french, nigerian
1. the nigerian is on the left of the french##1
2. the nigerian is between the french and the turkish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Nationality   | turkish | nigerian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
